data.title: Promising Actors & Actresses from Taiwan
data.text:
Amber An was born on 18 September 1985 in Taichung, Taiwan. She is an actress, known for Gû tshia lâi khì (2023), Kai chuang zhe (2023) and Xi men ding (2012).

Ariel Ann was born on 5 March 1985 in Taiwan. She is an actress, known for Game (2016), Angel 'n' Devil (2014) and Yi Dai Xin Bing Zhi Ba Ji Shao Nian (2015).

Bianca Bai was born on 23 October 1982 in Taipei, Taiwan. She is an actress, known for The Shinning Days (2009), Hua li de tiao zhan (2011) and Xiao shou qi ji (2016).

Larisa Bakurova was born on 21 February 1985 in Odessa, Ukrainian SSR, USSR [now Ukraine]. She is an actress, known for Ezuoju 2 wen (2007), Chao Ji Da Ying Xiong (2015) and Daan san nam nui (2011).

Derek Chang was born on 17 December 1992 in Taipei, Taiwan. He is an actor, known for My Dear Boy (2017), Light the Night (2021) and Fang Qi Wo, Zhua Jin Wo (2016).

Hsiao-chuan Chang was born on 28 December 1983 in Taiwan. He is an actor, known for Girlfriend Boyfriend (2012), Shi hun (2013) and Eternal Summer (2006). He has been married to wife since 1 December 2018. They have one child.

Ning Chang was born on 4 September 1982 in Taiwan. She is an actress and producer, known for The Abandoned (2022), Wennuan de xian (2018) and Da jun shi Si Ma Yi: Jun shi lian meng (2017).

Joe Shu-Wei Chang was born on 4 November 1980 in Taiwan. He is an actor, known for Luo ri (2015), Hei he zi (2016) and My Secret Garden (2003).

Michael Chang was born on 16 May 1980 in Taiwan. He is an actor, known for Siàu-lú pat-ka-tsiòng (2024), Bitter Sweet (2015) and White Robe of Love (2006).

Ning Chang was born on 4 December 1988 in Taiwan. She is an actress, known for Siàu lian ê (2022), Survival (2019) and Zhu li ye (2010).

Ray Chang was born on 31 March 1985 in Taiwan. He is an actor, known for Eternal Summer (2006), We Best Love: No.1 for You (2021) and When Geek Meets Serial Killer (2015). He has been married to Anruo Huang since 1 January 2019.

Shao-Huai Chang was born on 4 November 1980 in Taipei, Taiwan. He is an actor, known for Zheng hun qi shi (2014), Han bao yu zhui de mei yi tian (2013) and Qingtian jie yi hao (2015). He has been married to Hsin-yi Wong since July 2013. They have two children.

Mark Chao was born on 25 September 1984 in Taipei, Taiwan. He is an actor, known for Monga - Gangs of Taipeh (2010), Pi Zi Ying Xiong 2 (2014) and Yin-Yang Master I (2020). He has been married to Yuanyuan Gao since 5 June 2014. They have one child.

Allen Chen was born on 13 June 1984 in Taiwan. He is an actor, known for Di Yu Li Chang (2023), C.L.I.F. (2011) and I've Walked Through the Love's Wilderness (2022).

Andrea Chen was born on 20 November 1987 in Taipei, Taiwan. She is an actress, known for Wo ke neng bu hui ai ni (2011), Xi men ding (2012) and Prince William (2014).

Annie Chen was born on 28 April 1989 in Taichung, Taiwan. She is an actress, known for Sorry to Bother You (2018), Qing chun shi lian (2021) and Shi kong huang yan (2015).

Bolin Chen, a Taiwanese actor, is described as one of most talented young actors in Asian-Pacific region, a media label which he has received substantial attention. Chen gained immediate recognition in his first leading role as Zhang Shi-Hao in Blue Gate Crossing (2002). His performances in later films and TV series have been critically acclaimed and well received by the public, making Chen one of the most represented and popular actors in Taiwan.

Edward Chen was born on 2 August 1996 in Taichung, Taiwan. He is an actor, known for The Name Engraved in Your Heart (2020), Di Yu Li Chang (2023) and Xiao zi (2024).

Ella Chen was born on 18 June 1981 in Pingtung, Taiwan. She is an actress, known for Que jiao yi zu (2015), Zhen ming tian nu (2005) and Nu hai huai huai (2012). She has been married to Alvin Lai since 5 May 2012. They have one child.

Ikeya Chen was born on 11 August 1985 in Taipei, Taiwan. She is an actress, known for Zui jia li yi (2019), Juedui Daling (2012) and Xi li ren qi (2010).

Ivy Chen was born on 12 November 1982 in Taipei, Taiwan. She is an actress and director, known for Ting shuo (2009), Xiao xiao (2023) and Ai (2012). She has been married to Fu-Hsiang Hsu since 17 August 2018. They have two children.

Michelle Chen is a graduate of University of Southern California. She speaks English, Mandarin, and Taiwanese fluently, and a little bit Cantonese. She gained her initial fame in a minor role in the 2007 TV series Huan huan ai (2007) starring Rainie Yang. Michelle is best known for her starring role in the 2011 movie You are the Apple of my Eye (2011).
